(1, 'WebDevelopers', 'WorksForWeb', '<p>\r\nWorksForWeb is a classified software development company specialized in Web-based applications. Our team consists of business, marketing and software development professionals with ample software development skills and expertise.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWorksForWeb is the right choice for developing Web-based applications in various areas, with the special emphasis on the classifieds market. We offer three classified scripts:  <a href="http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iAuto/" title="iAuto">iAuto</a>, <a href="http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iRealty/" title="iRealty">iRealty</a> and <a href="http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iLister/" title="iLister">iLister</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAdditionally, we implement turnkey Web classified solutions, provide customization services for our products, and custom project development services.\r\n</p>', 'Please contact us at <a href="http://www.worksforweb.com/company/contact-us/">http://www.worksforweb.com/company/contact-us/</a>. You can skype us at iauto_irealty.', '', '+1 (202) 657-5939 ', NULL, 'sales@ilistersoft.com', 'http://www.worksforweb.com', '<p>\r\nAt WorkForWeb, we follow the agile software development paradigm. We believe that the most efficient way of building complex application is doing it the simplest way. Our approach to software is not bound by predefined procedures, processes, or steps. We use our best judgment and experience to identify the course of actions most appropriate for the current state of work.We often look back at our past experience to confirm the use of the best practices and avoid our past errors.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWe believe our success is solidly based on effective communication, customer collaboration, and common sense. We share the following values: simplicity, communication, feedback, and courage.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWe helped thousands people to create their on-line business based on our classified software: iAuto car classified software, iLister classified script and iRealty real estate script.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nToday we appreciate the opportunity to offer you to be our client. You can be an individual web developer, a representative of a Web studio, a business owner/manager or an e-businessperson looking for the software to built your own online classified project.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWe offer you a wide range of business solutions to allow you to run an online classifieds service with hundreds of users and tens of thousands records in the database. Please take a look at some <a href="http://www.worksforweb.com/company/portfolio/">examples</a> of how iAuto, iRealty and iLister classified software is used by our clients.\r\n</p>'),
(2, 'PetCare', 'Barkley Pet Hotel & Day Spa', '<p style="margin-top:8px;">\r\n	<strong>The Barkley Pet Hotel &amp; Day Spa</strong> is a resort-style vacation for <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/canine_quarters.aspx">dogs</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/kitty_city.aspx">cats</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/bird-boarding.aspx">birds and exotics</a>, which combines homelike amenities with recreational activity. Our inviting, state-of-the-art facility features a clean, secure and fun-filled environment - which meets and exceeds all kennel industry standards for <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/canine_quarters.aspx">boarding</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/pet-grooming/pet_grooming.aspx">grooming</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/">obedience training</a>, and <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/obedience-training/obedience-classes.aspx">doggie day camp</a>. Our trained and caring professionals provide unparalleled customer service and animal expertise to ensure the utmost in comfort, safety and happiness - 24-hours a day, 365 days a year; All while providing owners with incomparable peace-of-mind at an affordable price!</p>\r\n', '31166 Via Colinas, Westlake Village, California', '555555', '555555', NULL, 'info@westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com', 'http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com', '<p style="margin-top:8px;">\r\n	<strong>The Barkley Pet Hotel &amp; Day Spa</strong> is a resort-style vacation for <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/canine_quarters.aspx">dogs</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/kitty_city.aspx">cats</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/bird-boarding.aspx">birds and exotics</a>, which combines homelike amenities with recreational activity. Our inviting, state-of-the-art facility features a clean, secure and fun-filled environment - which meets and exceeds all kennel industry standards for <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/accommodations/canine_quarters.aspx">boarding</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/pet-grooming/pet_grooming.aspx">grooming</a>, <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/">obedience training</a>, and <a href="http://westlake.thebarkleypethotel.com/obedience-training/obedience-classes.aspx">doggie day camp</a>. Our trained and caring professionals provide unparalleled customer service and animal expertise to ensure the utmost in comfort, safety and happiness - 24-hours a day, 365 days a year; All while providing owners with incomparable peace-of-mind at an affordable price!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The new 32,000 square foot Barkley Pet Hotel &amp; Day Spa allows owners to choose from a variety of spacious overnight accommodations for their pets - ranging from traditional guest rooms to luxury suites complete with flat screen televisions, web cam access and leather furniture. The guest services menu makes sure each pet stays active with an array of activity options designed to fit every lifestyle. The salon &amp; day spa offers simple spa baths to full body massages and &quot;pawdicures&quot;. And, the day camp is a cage-free, dog-friendly outlet to expend excess energy, socialize and exercise.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The Barkley is located at 31166 Via Colinas in Westlake Village, California. It is housed alongside a brand new, technologically-advanced <a href="http://www.westlakevet.com/">Westlake Village Animal Hospital</a>. Providing 24-hour (on-call), 7 day a week, emergency veterinary service, Dr. Daniel Slaton and Dr. Steven Rosenstein of WVAH provide the highest level of veterinary care. This is just another reason that The Barkley Pet Hotel &amp; Day Spa is America&#39;s premiere pet care facility.</p>\r\n');
